                  </persName>
            ; on the 15th of July last, we lost two pair of sheets; I was sitting in my bar; we <rs id="t17900915-53-viclabel287" type="occupation">keep a publick-house</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900915-53-victim567 t17900915-53-viclabel287"></join>; he was turning the stairs; I ran after a young man, and told him to run after him; the prisoner had a bundle before him; he was taken; I did not see him taken; it was between nine and ten at night; there was a great coat, and waistcoat and breeches, and silk handkerchief, belonging to Mr. Sutton; the sheets belonged to us; the great coat lay by the bed-side; the sheets were in the same room, the two pair of stairs; I gave them to the watchman, 
